                            <comment id="18023792" author="JIRAUSER305622" created="Tue, 30 Sep 2025 12:08:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The root cause of this is the customization of the colors of the Tab element. by overriding the values and the background, it does no longer highlight correctly the elements.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To solve this I would try to correctly apply the colors, eventually by even replacing the Tab element with a better suited UI element, and take into account all states, including enabled, disabled, hovered, focused and selected. I believe a ToggleButton may cover all our needs, with potentially small adjustments. See also feedback on PR why I would prefer not to use custom borders.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
